text: Washington Department of Children, Youth, and Families (DYCF) is an agency of the State of Washington, United States focusing on services for children. It was created by House Bill 1661, which was signed by Governor Jay Inslee on July 6, 2017. ==References== ==External links== * Washington Department of Children, Youth, and Families Category:State agencies of Washington (state)
